
                        / Caster /

       Listen to and tracker your podcasts anywhere


    ~ What is Caster?

      A MongoDB and Flask powered podcast tracker

    ~ How do I use it?

      1. edit the configuration in the caster.py file or
         export an CASTER_SETTINGS environment variable
         pointing to a configuration file.

      2. fire up a python shell and run this:

         >>> from caster import init_db; init_db()

      3. now you can run the caster.py file with your
         python interpreter and the application will
         greet you on http://localhost
